snippet.textDisplay: Hum main sy kisi musalmaan main itna bara dil ni k hum keertan bhajan christian pryers ya deegar mazahib k kosi kalam ko sunain Allah rehem kary un per jinhoon ny iss hamd ko talhleek kiya iss anddaz sy k ghair muslims ttak jo shaoor rakhty hain ya ni wo isy sun rahy hain aur appreciate kr ry hain aur ek hamain dekho koi unhain sikha ra hai k ye naat hai ya hamd unhain iss sy matlab ni k ye kya parha ja ra hai unhain ye gharz hai k kon aur kesy parh raha hai unhain hamd aur naat k chakkar main na dalo ho sakta hai k koi khud he impress ho k matlab pooch baithy. Kehty hain jab ilm ki talab ho ttab he diya jaay warna bina mangy diay gay ilm ko zaya karny k barabar hai hum pakistani sary ni mager kuch aisy hain k hamesha relevent forum pe irrelevant behes shuru kar jaty hain kosi zuban sy majaal jo Masha Allah nikla ho ek ghair muslim bhai ny poory lyrics likhy logoon ki asani k liay pata ni un ka kitna waqt laga hoga anjan zuban ko samajhny aur likhny main mager hamary ek muhtaram ny unki kavish ko sarahny k bajaay keh diya k iss main kafi sari ghalatiyan hain bhai sarahna seekho aur jo baat jis forum pe karni ho karo. Main un tamam ahl e kitab aur deeger mazahib k followers ka bohot shukar guzar hoon apni tamam muslaman ummat ki taraf sy jonhoon ny iss kalam ko suna aur saraha be shak Allah ki zaat kisi ki tareef ki mohtaaj naheen mager khalik ko apni makhlook ki zuban sy apni barae aun k acha lagta hai ghar main bivi k khany ki tareef karo tto usy acha lagta hai na karo tto next day dhaaby sy khao bus CS ny bhe apny anddaz sy tareef ki Allah iska ajar unhain iss aur uss dono dunyaoon main apni raheemi kareemi k hisab sy ddy aur un tamam k hak main jinhoon ny iss kalam ko suna sarha koi aisa fesla kary jis sy uni ye aur wo duniya behter ho. Jazak Allah o khair
